androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
com.example.butter.HomeAdminFragment
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, androidx.activity.result.ActivityResultCaller, androidx.lifecycle.HasDefaultViewModelProviderFactory, androidx.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, androidx.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, androidx.savedstate.SavedStateRegistryOwner, ConfirmationDialog.ConfirmationDialogListener
public class HomeAdminFragment extends androidx.fragment.app.Fragment implements ConfirmationDialog.ConfirmationDialogListener
This fragment is used to set up the home screen on the admins side. Admins have access to a spinner and can also access entrants page.
